## 0.5 NEW bugs discovered during the fix (not yet fixed)
- [x] FIXED 2026-07-22: `workers/billing-sync.ts` (5├Ч) + `workers/email-send.ts` (1├Ч) audit_log
      INSERTs used a nonexistent `metadata` column тЖТ remapped to `new_data` (schema-correct)
- [x] FIXED 2026-07-22: `generate-monthly` (route + rent-generate worker) тАФ confirmed the
      `ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING` matched NO constraint (only UNIQUE was idempotency_key = NULL)
      тЖТ re-runs would duplicate every student's rent. Added migration 008
      (`uq_payments_student_month` partial unique index), explicit conflict targets,
      pre-check that skips already-billed students WITHOUT burning receipt numbers,
      `Number()` coercion on monthly_fee (string concat тЖТ 10├Ч rent), and an audit row
      for bulk generation. тЪая╕П Migration 008 must be applied to any live DB.
